'''珊瑚白化'''现象是[[珊瑚礁|珊瑚礁]]所表现出来的病理特征，造成珊瑚白化的原因有很多，除最主要的[[全球变暖|全球变暖]]而导致的[[暖流|暖流]]匯聚導致[[海水|海水]][[溫度|溫度]]過高<ref name="theguardian.com">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2016/jun/07/the-great-barrier-reef-a-catastrophe-laid-bare|title=The Great Barrier Reef: a catastrophe laid bare|date=2016-06-06|newspaper=The Guardian|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|access-date=2016-10-15|archive-date=2020-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106185850/https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2016/jun/07/the-great-barrier-reef-a-catastrophe-laid-bare|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Temp>{{cite web|title=REEF 'AT RISK IN CLIMATE CHANGE' |url=http://www.coralcoe.org.au/news_stories/climatechange.html |accessdate=2007-07-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070801020136/http://www.coralcoe.org.au/news_stories/climatechange.html |archivedate=2007-08-01 }}</ref><ref name=KAnthony>Anthony, K. 2007; Berkelmans</ref><ref name=TSaxby2003>{{Cite journal | last1 = Saxby | first1 = T. | last2 = Dennison | first2 = W. C. | last3 = Hoegh-Guldberg | first3 = O. | title = Photosynthetic responses of the coral Montipora digitata to cold temperature stress | doi = 10.3354/meps248085 | journal = Marine Ecology Progress Series | volume = 248 | page = 85 | year = 2003 | pmid =  | pmc = }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=Marimuthu, N. |author2=Wilson, J. Jerald |author3=Vinithkumar, N. V. |author4=Kirubagaran, R. |year=2012 |title=Coral reef recovery status in south Andaman Islands after the bleaching event 2010 |journal=Journal of Ocean University of China |volume=12 |issue=1 |pages=91–96 |doi=10.1007/s11802-013-2014-2 |bibcode = 2013JOUC...12...91M }}</ref>，诸如沉積物增加（包含[[泥|泥]][[沙|沙]]）而引起水變混濁<ref>{{cite journal |author=Rogers, S.R. |title=Responses of coral reefs and reef organisms to sedimentation |journal=Marine Ecology Progress Series |volume=62 |pages=185–202 |year=1990 |url=http://www.int-res.com/articles/meps/62/m062p185.pdf |doi=10.3354/meps062185 |access-date=2016-06-20 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065204/http://www.int-res.com/articles/meps/62/m062p185.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[細菌|細菌]]感染<ref>{{cite journal  |author=Kushmaro, A., Rosenberg, E., Fine, M., Loya, Y.  |title=l Beaching of the coral Oculina patagonica by Vibrio AK-1  |journal=Marine Ecology Progress Series  |volume=147  |pages=159–165  |year=1997  |url=http://www.tau.ac.il/lifesci/departments/zoology/members/loya/1108.pdf.pdf  |doi=10.3354/meps147159  |last2=Rosenberg  |last3=Fine  |last4=Loya  |access-date=2016-06-20  |archive-date=2016-03-03  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234524/http://www.tau.ac.il/lifesci/departments/zoology/members/loya/1108.pdf.pdf  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>、海水中[[除草剂|除草剂]]浓度增高<ref>{{cite journal|author=Jones, R.J., Muller, J., Haynes, D., Schrieber, U., |title=Effects of herbicides diuron and atrazine on corals of the Great Barrier Reef, Australia |journal=Marine Ecology Progress Series |volume=251 |pages=153–167 |year=2003 |url=http://www.bios-mep.info/(2003)%20Jones,%20Muller,%20Haynes,%20Schreiber%20-%20Marine%20Ecology%20Progress%20Series.pdf |doi=10.3354/meps251153 |last2=Muller |last3=Haynes |last4=Schreiber |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100331074104/http://www.bios-mep.info/%282003%29%20Jones%2C%20Muller%2C%20Haynes%2C%20Schreiber%20-%20Marine%20Ecology%20Progress%20Series.pdf |archivedate=2010-03-31 }}</ref>、海水鹽度改變<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Hoegh-Guldberg, O. |author2=Smith, G.J. |title=The effect of sudden changes in temperature, light and salinity on the population density and export of zooxanthellae from the reef corals Stylophora pistillata Esper and Seriatopora hystrix Dana |journal=Journal of Experimental Marine Biology and Ecology |volume=129 |pages=279–303 |year=1989 |url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0022098189901093 |doi=10.1016/0022-0981(89)90109-3 |issue=3 |access-date=2016-06-20 |archive-date=2016-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106075527/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0022098189901093 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、海水中的化學反應的变化<ref name=Johnson07>{{cite book|first1=Johanna E |last1=Johnson |first2=Paul A |last2=Marshall |title=Climate change and the Great Barrier Reef: a vulnerability assessment |publisher=Great Barrier Reef Marine Park Authority |location=Townsville, Qld. |year=2007 |isbn=978-1-876945-61-9 |url=http://www.gbrmpa.gov.au/resources-and-publications/publications/climate-change-and-the-great-barrier-reef-a-vulnerability-assessment |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125180404/http://www.gbrmpa.gov.au/resources-and-publications/publications/climate-change-and-the-great-barrier-reef-a-vulnerability-assessment |archivedate=2014-01-25 }}</ref><ref name="Hoegh-Guldberg O, Mumby PJ, Hooten AJ, et al. 2007 1737–42">{{cite journal |author=Hoegh-Guldberg O, Mumby PJ, Hooten AJ |title=Coral reefs under rapid climate change and ocean acidification |journal=Science |volume=318 |issue=5857 |pages=1737–42 |date=December 2007 |pmid=18079392 |doi=10.1126/science.1152509 |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=18079392|author2=and others |displayauthors=1 |bibcode=2007Sci...318.1737H |last3=Hooten |last4=Steneck |last5=Greenfield |last6=Gomez |last7=Harvell |last8=Sale |last9=Edwards |last10=Caldeira |last11=Knowlton |last12=Eakin |last13=Iglesias-Prieto |last14=Muthiga |last15=Bradbury |last16=Dubi |last17=Hatziolos }}</ref>、太陽的輻射量（光合活性放射線和[[紫外線|紫外線]]）的增加以及退潮和曝光等<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Anthony, K.R.N. |author2=Kerswell, A.P. |title=Coral mortality following extreme low tides and high solar radiation |journal=Marine Ecology Progress Series |volume=151 |issue=5 |pages=1623–1631 |year=2007 |url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/br08wn7w147166t3/ |doi=10.1007/s00227-006-0573-0 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>也可能造成珊瑚白化现象<ref>{{cite web |title=為什麼珊瑚會白化？ |url=http://edresource.nmns.edu.tw/ShowObject.aspx?id=0b81d9d8160b81d9d2990b81b762a50b81b7649b |publisher=[[國立自然科學博物館|國立自然科學博物館]]學習網 |date= |accessdate=2016-06-20 |archive-date=2016-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817215700/http://edresource.nmns.edu.tw/ShowObject.aspx?id=0b81d9d8160b81d9d2990b81b762a50b81b7649b |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

珊瑚是[[珊瑚虫|珊瑚虫]]和其体内[[海藻|海藻]]的[[共生|共生]]体<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalcoralbleaching.org/#essential-facts |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-11-09 |archive-date=2017-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171114151304/http://www.globalcoralbleaching.org/#essential-facts |dead-url=no }}</ref>。健康的珊瑚會出現紅、黃、綠、藍、紫等各種美麗的顏色，而這些顏色其实其体内海藻的颜色。白化的珊瑚会排出体内的海藻，从而显现出白色。海藻通过[[光合作用|光合作用]]为珊瑚带来90% 能量，而长期失去海藻的珊瑚虫也会由于饥饿而造成大面积死亡<ref name="theguardian.com"/> 。而珊瑚礁具有很高的[[生态多样性|生态多样性]]，其仅占海洋面积的1%左右，却提供着海洋中超过25%的[[鱼类|鱼类]]赖以生存的[[生态系统|生态系统]]<ref>{{cite web|title= Value of Coral Ecosystems|url= https://coralreef.noaa.gov/aboutcorals/values/biodiversity/|date= |accessdate= 2017-11-09|archive-date= 2017-12-21|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20171221042227/https://coralreef.noaa.gov/aboutcorals/values/biodiversity/|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite video|title=How dead is the Great Barrier Reef?|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BO44JlAElXM|date=|accessdate=2017-11-09|archive-date=2017-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171101211356/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BO44JlAElXM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。珊瑚礁的破坏与死亡，是对海洋生态系统的巨大挑战。

珊瑚礁对海水的温度非常敏感，在持续几周的2[[摄氏度|摄氏度]]左右的海水升温状态中，其体内的海藻开始大量囤积[[过氧化氢|过氧化氢]]，而过氧化氢会同珊瑚礁岩发生化学反应，珊瑚虫为了保护自己，不得不将海藻排出体外<ref name="#1"/>从而造成珊瑚白化现象。庆幸的是，这些珊瑚虫并不会马上死亡，如果接下来海水降温足够快，这些海藻会在几周内重新被珊瑚虫吸收体内。如若不然，死亡后珊瑚礁的恢复期可能会长达十年以上。

==大規模白化事件==
大多數的證據都證明高溫是造成珊瑚白化的主因，1979～1990年期間發生超過60種誘發珊瑚白化的因素<ref name=Chumkiew>{{cite journal|title=Impact of Global Warming on Coral Reefs|last=Chumkiew|first=Sirilak|via=ResearchGate|date=2011|url=http://www.researchgate.net/publication/259578623_Impact_of_Global_Warming_on_Coral_Reefs|accessdate=2014-02-27|journal=|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518090613/http://www.researchgate.net/publication/259578623_Impact_of_Global_Warming_on_Coral_Reefs|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Huppert|first=Amit|author2=Lewis Stone|title=Chaos in the Pacific's Coral Reef Bleaching Cycle|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-naturalist_1998-09_152_3/page/447|journal=The American Naturalist|date=September 1998|volume=152|issue=3|pages=447–459|doi=10.1086/286181|pmid=18811451}}</ref>。歷史上有紀錄首次發生大規模的珊瑚白化現象是在1980年代早期，而首次全球性的白化現象是從1997年夏季持續至1998年。

根據詹姆斯-庫克大學ARC珊瑚卓越研究中心休斯教授的說法，對[[湯斯維爾|湯斯維爾]]和[[巴布亞新幾內亞|巴布亞新幾內亞]]之間的大堡礁北部和中部84種[[珊瑚|珊瑚]]進行調查，有35%的珊瑚現在已死亡或正在死亡，由於[[全球暖化|全球暖化]]，連續第三年[[大堡礁|大堡礁]]出現大規模珊瑚白化現象<ref>{{cite news |title=大堡礁：珊瑚白化現象「令35%珊瑚死亡」 |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2016/05/160530_great_barrier_reef_bleaching_kills |newspaper=BBC中文新聞網 |publisher= |date=2016-05-30 |accessdate=2016-06-20 |archive-date=2016-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602061048/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2016/05/160530_great_barrier_reef_bleaching_kills |dead-url=no }}</ref>。如今世界的每一個角落幾乎都跟珊瑚白化有關聯，統計至2016年的夏天已有多處國家的近海中的珊瑚皆受到白化的影響。
在1998年和2004年的聖嬰現象過程中海水水溫超過了一般情況，許多珊瑚礁出現了白化的現象，有些死亡。此後部分離污染源遠的地區的珊瑚礁獲得恢復。但是也有些學者認為由於全球暖化造成的珊瑚礁的擴展會高於其死亡，許多不應該出現珊瑚的地方，例如日本列島南部，已經出現了熱帶珊瑚。有人甚至估計到2100年全球珊瑚礁的面積會比工業革命前增長35%。

==影響區域==
===大堡礁===
統計至2016年5月31日，大堡礁受到珊瑚白化影響的年度為1980、1982、1992、1994、1998、2002、2006以及2016年<ref name=Plumer>{{cite web|last=Plumer|first=Brad|title=The unprecedented coral bleaching disaster at the Great Barrier Reef, explained|url=http://www.vox.com/2016/3/30/11332636/great-barrier-reef-coral-bleaching|work=Vox Energy & Environment|accessdate=2016-03-31|archive-date=2016-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401025040/http://www.vox.com/2016/3/30/11332636/great-barrier-reef-coral-bleaching|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有些地方的生態遭到嚴重的破壞，珊瑚死亡的機率提高至9成<ref name=Johnson07 />。1992年至2002年的夏天珊瑚白化影響力最為普遍及活躍，珊瑚白化的機率約42至54%，還有18%珊瑚強烈白化的機率<ref name=Done>{{cite book|vauthors=Done T, Whetton P, Jones R, Berkelmans R, Lough J, Skirving W, Wooldridge S |title=Global Climate Change and Coral Bleaching on the Great Barrier Reef |publisher=Queensland Government Department of Natural Resources and Mines |year=2003 |isbn=0-642-32220-1 |url=http://www.hutten.org/fw/docs/319.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927221700/http://www.hutten.org/fw/docs/319.pdf |archivedate=2011-09-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Berkelmans R, De'ath G, Kininmonth S, Skirving WJ |title=A comparison of the 1998 and 2002 coral bleaching events on the Great Barrier Reef: spatial correlation, patterns, and predictions |journal=Coral Reefs |volume=23 |issue=1 |pages=74–83 |date=April 2004 |doi=10.1007/s00338-003-0353-y |url=http://www.springerlink.com/index/WVF2DEAGMR0TV5TA.pdf |last2=De'Ath |last3=Kininmonth |last4=Skirving }}{{Dead link|date=2020年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>；1995年至2002年期間珊瑚白化的機率較低，其中一個原因是有新珊瑚成長的機率略高的關係所導致<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.plosone.org/article/info:doi%2F10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0017516|title= Disturbance and the Dynamics of Coral Cover on the Great Barrier Reef (1995–2009)|accessdate= 2016-06-20|archive-date= 2014-12-17|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141217064201/http://www.plosone.org/article/info:doi%2F10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0017516|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

